%^BOLD%^-=%^MAGENTA%^Hedonism Domain%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

Indulging in the pursuit of pleasure, the hedonism domain allows the cleric to share in experiences and draw on the desires of those around them.

Clerics with the Hedonism Domain gain the following benefits:
- A +1 to caster level when casting spells of the enchantment_charm sphere if you are intoxicated.
- A +1 to spell DC when casting spells of the enchantment_charm sphere if you are intoxicated.

The hedonism domain contains the following spells:

Alter Self, Captivate, Drunken Stupor, Kiss of Torment, Scintillating Pattern

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Cacia

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^